</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/kotaku/vip/~4/9X-6D9NLOX0" height="1" width="1"/>";s:14:"date_timestamp";i:1331607540;}i:3;a:11:{s:5:"title";s:30:"Soul Vaccination [Open Thread]";s:11:"description";s:3285:"<p><img src="http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/17g97hvcvhs9ujpg/medium.jpg" width="300" class="image_0 v10_medium" alt="Soul Vaccination"  title="Soul Vaccination" />Greetings <em>Kotaku</em>-eers, and welcome to a new week of evening open threads. I missed doing these last week during the Game Developers Conference! It's good to be back.</p>
<p>Below, please find a collection of things that you might enjoy checking out or talking about. The Tower of Power tune, in particular, is worthy of a listen.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=buqtdpuZxvk">Monty Python's "The Galaxy Song"</a> - Whenever life gets you down, Mrs. Brown...</li>
<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5msQ3Z_UcoI&feature=share">Tower of Power: "On the serious side"</a> Damn it. So tight.</li>
