<div style="float: left; width: 300px; margin: 10px 10px 0px 0px; font-size: 0.675em; color: grey); padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;"><a rel="lytebox" href="http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/17g7iyrn3h5fujpg/original.jpg"><img src="http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/17g7iyrn3h5fujpg/medium.jpg" width="300" class="image_1 v10_medium" alt="Where are the Black League of Legends Characters?"  title="Where are the Black League of Legends Characters?" /></a><br>
