<div class="modfont" style="float: right; width: 190px; margin: 10px 0px 10px 25px; line-height: 0.85em; font-size: 1.85em; color: black; padding: 16px;">If online experiences like <em>StarCraft</em> and <em>League of Legends</em> can constantly evolve based on community feedback, why can't their stories?</div>
