<p>You want to go to space, don't you? Or at least the top of this page, right? If you want Snifkin-style glory, here's what you do. Post your masterpieces in the <a href="http://kotaku.com/taypics/forum">#TAYpics thread</a>. Don't forget to keep your image in a 16x9 ratio if you want a slice of Talk Amongst Yourselves glory. Grab the base image <a href="%20http://img.gawkerassets.com/post/9/2012/03/the_hunters_at_rest_by_vasily_perov.jpg">here</a>. The best ones will be featured in future installments of Talk Amongst Yourselves. Get cracking!</p><div class="feedflare">
