<p>Joyce's remains were eventually discovered when building officials entered her apartment to repossess it. They found her skeleton where she'd last sat, television still playing in front of her, presents still nearby, though quite a bit more dusty. That discovery happened&mdash;someone finally found out that Joyce had passed away from apparently natural causes&mdash;in January of 2006.</p>
