<p><a rel="lytebox" href="http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/17g7o8ak6bd4ejpg/original.jpg"><img src="http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/17g7o8ak6bd4ejpg/medium.jpg" width="300" class="image_1 v10_medium" alt="A Normal Life, An Extraordinary Death and the Video Game That Wasn't Meant to Be"  title="A Normal Life, An Extraordinary Death and the Video Game That Wasn't Meant to Be" /></a>Several years ago, the big mystery of Joyce's death and the many mysteries of her life propelled filmmaker Carol Morley to find Joyce's friends and loved ones to make a documentary about this no-longer-forgotten woman.</p>
