<a rel="lytebox" href="http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/17g7a693netlipng/original.png"><img src="http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/17g7a693netlipng/medium.png" width="300" class="image_4 v10_medium" alt="At This Chinese Video Game Bar, You Drink"  title="At This Chinese Video Game Bar, You Drink" /></a></p><div class="feedflare">
